sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant KVCache as KV-Cache Manager<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request Routing

    Client->>Gateway: POST / (inference request)<br/>HTTP/80, No Auth
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002, plaintext
    Note over EPP: Plugin Pipeline:<br/>1. Filters narrow candidates<br/>(ByLabel, ByLabelSelector)<br/>2. Scorers rank pods<br/>(PrefixCache, LoadAware,<br/>SessionAffinity)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod list & status
    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc response<br/>Selected pod endpoint
    Gateway->>vLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000, plaintext
    vLLM-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D Mode)

    Client->>Gateway: POST / (inference request)<br/>HTTP/80, No Auth
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002, plaintext
    Note over EPP: PdProfileHandler:<br/>1. Run decode profile<br/>(DecodeFilter + Scorers)<br/>2. Run prefill profile<br/>(PrefillFilter + Scorers)
    Note over EPP: PrefillHeaderHandler:<br/>Sets x-prefiller-host-port
    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc response<br/>Decode pod + prefill header
    Gateway->>vLLM: Forward to decode pod<br/>HTTP/8000, x-prefiller-host-port set
    vLLM-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over EPP,KVCache: Flow 3: KV-Cache Tracking Event Stream

    KVCache->>EPP: KV-cache events<br/>ZMQ SUB/5557, plaintext
    Note over EPP: KV-Events Pool updates<br/>PrefixCacheTracking scorer<br/>uses real-time cache state
